title: Gainesville's Emily House places sixth at US Powerlifting Nationals
text:
Gainesville's Emily House places sixth at US Powerlifting Nationals Times sports reports POSTED: October 20, 2015 5:37 p.m. For The Times/ View Larger 
Gainesvilleâ€™s Emily House placed sixth recently at the US Powerlifting National Championships in Scranton, Pennsylvania. 
Lifting in the 72 kilogram class, House lifted 220 pounds on the bench press, squated 291 pounds and deadlifted 414. 
Her total of 925 was 49 more than in qualifying for the Nationals. Comments No comments have been posted.
